      "supporting_facts": "Subacute encephalopathy and multifocal MRI findings.",
      "opposing_facts": "CSF protein is only mildly elevated, and there is no evidence of leptomeningeal enhancement or infarcts in multiple arterial territories that would typically suggest vasculitis.",
      "support_level": "Weakly supported"
    },
